  "description": "MEANtools is a computational pipeline that integrates multi-omics data to identify metabolites and predict biosynthetic pathways\n\nhttps://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2024.12.22.629970v1\n\nThis repository contains data for the meantools repository https://github.com/kumarsaurabh20/meantools\u00a0\n\nData:\n\n\n\nLotus database in SQLite format\n\nRetroRules formatted data (loose, medium, and strict datasets)\u00a0\n\nEC-pfam IDs map\n\nRNA-seq expression matrix (normalized) from Jeon et al. 2020\n\nJeon_bacterial.sqlite (output of gene-metabolite correlations, calculated edge-scores and functional clusters for Bacterial samples)\n\nJeon_Fungal.sqlite (output of gene-metabolite correlations, calculated edge-scores and functional clusters for Fungal samples)",
